# Admin API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = your_admin_jwt_token_here

### Admin Login (First create admin user manually in database or use auth register)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@university.edu",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Get Admin Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Users with Filter (Students only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?role=student&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Search Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?search=john&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get User Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update User Status (Activate/Deactivate)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/USER_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

###

### Get All Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Orders with Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders?status=pending&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get All Restaurants
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update Restaurant Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

###

### Create New Admin User
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/create-admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Admin",
  "email": "newadmin@university.edu",
  "password": "newadmin123"
}

###

### Get Analytics (7 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/analytics?period=7days
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Analytics (30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/analytics?period=30days
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Analytics (3 months)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/analytics?period=3months
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
